{"tid":2403064,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人嘅迷信文化 大多都係源於諧音 盡顯幾千年文化係幾膚淺兒戲","createTime":"2021-02-11T01:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T10:22:17.000Z","uid":82312,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f61f0ca968f822b8a3441267cc285411033cac9","tid":2403064,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:06:56.000Z","msg":"又話中國文化幾千年歷史<br />\n又博大精心又性<br />\n一到啲大時大節就盡顯劣根文化完全係膚淺低質<br />\n<br />\n新年放盤桔 因為&ldquo;吉&rdquo;利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通書 輸輸聲 叫通勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要食髮菜 因為發財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食蠔屎 因為好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以放梅花 因為會&ldquo;霉&rdquo;足一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以買鞋 唉唉聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔洗用腦都知道係點黎<br />\n兒戲膚淺到不得了<br />\n但仲要可以流傳到2021年都仲有人信<br />\n好難怪幾千年都比啲幾百年國家超越<br />\n完全冇文化可言<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2663643761ee264ffdc04152cb4d97e56e4d72","tid":2403064,"uid":60881,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:07:50.000Z","msg":"中個文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6f2194ae7442c073ceee88555e9acf6decd452","tid":2403064,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"咁我覺得公平啲<br />\n諧音講意頭就成個東亞都係咁嘅"},{"pid":"da0ab15b8699813ae3869f3de74f6bc47047ca94","tid":2403064,"uid":144001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:14:35.000Z","msg":"戇鳩民族 唔滅都冇用啦"},{"pid":"a1e777d5623c967af70c62eba316a4788c8ef065","tid":2403064,"uid":68098,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"其實世界各地都有<br />\n<br />\n因為大部份文化都認為<br />\n人既說話<br />\n或多或少<br />\n都帶一點<b